1) -> Encapsulation means wrapping up the implementation of the data members and methods in a class.

2) -> Encapsulation solves the implementation level issues.

3) -> Encapsulation is used to hide the complexity or programs.

4) -> Abstraction means hiding unnecessary details and showing valuable information.

5) -> Abstraction solves the design level issues.

6) -> Data hiding is used for data security along with hiding the complexity of program.

